style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Parameter-free and auto-adaptive methodologies for personal
          analytics</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Novel indicators measuring personal behavior</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Individual vs. collective models</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Privacy-preserving mining algorithm</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Privacy-preserving individual data sharing</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Privacy risk assessment</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Privacy and anonymity in collective services</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Information (data/patterns) hiding</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Privacy in pervasive/ubiquitous systems</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Security and privacy metrics</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Personal data protection and law enforcement</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Balancing privacy and quality of the service/analysis</span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><br
            class="kix-line-break">
        </span><span
style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Times;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">•
          Case study analysis and experiments on real individual data</span></p>
      <p dir="ltr"
style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:1.4pt;margin-bottom:13.5pt;background-color:#ffffff;"><span
